# Email mapping for Git/GitHub contributor attribution
# Format: Proper Name <proper@email> Wrong Name <wrong@email>
# This file helps normalize author names and exclude bots from contributors list

# Exclude Dependabot from contributors
# Dependabot commits are automation, not human contributions
<dependabot[bot]@users.noreply.github.com> dependabot[bot] <dependabot[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
<dependabot-preview[bot]@users.noreply.github.com> dependabot-preview[bot] <dependabot-preview[bot]@users.noreply.github.com>
